cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.RO 

The paper deals with object segmentation in aerial videos using deep learning techniques. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also proposes a hierarchical approach that involves training two-stream CNNs, which falls under the category of deep learning and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of CNNs for segmentation also involves optimization and training, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also deals with video processing, which falls under the category of multimedia (cs.MM). Finally, the paper deals with unmanned aerial vehicles, which falls under the category of robotics (cs.RO).
